{"tid":1331694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳香港示威者赴台尋庇護　蔡英文：會基於人道適當處理","createTime":"2019-07-19T04:44:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T05:22:06.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0265b970108a63efb71612b83ea67509cbd7d1f8","tid":1331694,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T04:44:21.000Z","msg":"立場報道2019/7/19 &mdash; 11:23<br />\n7 月 1 日有大批示威者衝擊立法會，有報道指有十多名香港示威者抵達台灣，正接觸台灣陸委會希望尋求庇護。台灣總統蔡英文近日出訪聖露西亞，她接受傳媒訪問時表示，相信有關單位掌握情況，對於這些來自香港的朋友，會基於人道作適當處理。<br />\n<br />\n多家台媒昨晚（18日）引述陸委會回應傳聞指，若政府有收到相關申請個案，會在尊重人權保障與人道關懷原則下，由相關機關參酌相關法規，就個案需求妥適處理。陸委會又表示，支持香港的民主自由及保障人權，是台灣各界的一貫立場。<br />\n<br />\n陸委會又指，依「香港澳門關係條例」及相關辦法規定，對於香港居民來台，不論是停留或居留均有所規範。至於因政治因素致安全及自由受有緊急危害的香港居民，也會提供必要協助。<br />\n<br />\n但陸委會並未證實有否接觸示威者及確切人數。<br />\n<br />\n《自由亞洲電台》昨日報道，指從多個官方和非官方消息渠道證實，十多名香港示威者已抵達台灣。一名不願透露姓名的台灣律師正協助這些示威者，他相信這批人要申請延長居留台灣，技術上會有困難，因為他們未被香港警方拘捕或檢控，而且他們當時都帶了口罩，無法向台灣方面證明他們衝擊過立法會。<br />\n<br />\n相關報道：<br />\n<br />\n中央通訊社／東森新聞／聯合新聞網<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%82%B3%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E8%B5%B4%E5%8F%B0%E5%B0%8B%E5%BA%87%E8%AD%B7-%E8%94%A1%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87-%E6%9C%83%E5%9F%BA%E6%96%BC%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%93%E9%81%A9%E7%95%B6%E8%99%95%E7%90%86/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2582%25B3%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%25B5%25B4%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%25B0%258B%25E5%25BA%2587%25E8%25AD%25B7-%25E8%2594%25A1%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%2596%2587-%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%259F%25BA%25E6%2596%25BC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2581%2593%25E9%2581%25A9%25E7%2595%25B6%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%2590%2586%2F&d=4e%2FpP7P6HSNE6mjGPWQpDQ1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=27f8b63e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2582%25B3%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%25B5%25B4%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%25B0%258B%25E5%25BA%2587%25E8%25AD%25B7-%25E8%2594%25A1%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%2596%2587-%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%259F%25BA%25E6%2596%25BC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2581%2593%25E9%2581%25A9%25E7%2595%25B6%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%2590%2586%2F&h=4dbd4752\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%82%B3%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E8%B5%B4%E5%8F%B0%E5%B0%8B%E5%BA%87%E8%AD%B7-%E8%94%A1%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87-%E6%9C%83%E5%9F%BA%E6%96%BC%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%93%E9%81%A9%E7%95%B6%E8%99%95%E7%90%86/</a>"},{"pid":"ee481471ee9f71e87087580b623a07a23bcb7b1d","tid":1331694,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T04:47:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jGem6Rf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjGem6Rf.png&h=b24b8c13&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j5pY84L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj5pY84L.png&h=3ded51ad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mijY84T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmijY84T.png&h=82615ae4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07d745af7803b86c7ee61f6be275d9be7f027781","tid":1331694,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T05:22:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}